N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6219.3 - No New State Law Entitlement

State Regulations

Nothing herein shall be construed to permit a voter who does
not meet the requirements for voter registration provided for in Article 5 of
the Election law to receive a ballot containing state or local
offices. Notes
